T02TD3702E:336a-0: @336a * // nor rgyun ma'i smon lam bzhugs//
T02TD3702E:336a-2: # // sangs rgyas la gus rang bzhin g-yo sgyu med //
T02TD3702E:336a-3: sems can kun la byams shing stong par goms //
T02TD3702E:336a-4: rnam grol 'bras bur ldan la kun nas chags //
T02TD3702E:336a-5: byang chub sems dpa'i shes rab rno ba can //
T02TD3702E:336a-6: shin tu che ba'i rigs skyes gzugs mdzes pa //
T02TD3702E:336a-7: bdag ni skye ba skye bar bde gshegs kyi //
T02TD3702E:336a-8: snyan dngags mkhan po mnyam med rgya chen dang //
T02TD3702E:336a-9: tshe ring rigs skye skyes bu blo gros gsal //
T02TD3702E:336a-10: mkhas shing blo gros mi dman bcom ldan gyi //
T02TD3702E:336a-11: gsung rab la mkhas bde ldan snying rje can //
T02TD3702E:336a-12: rab tu dang 'gyur snyan dngags mkhan po dang //
T02TD3702E:336a-13: mar shes pha ma la gus nyid dang ni //
T02TD3702E:336a-14: rtag tu skye ba dran zhing tshul khrims ldan //
T02TD3702E:336a-15: chos kyi bdag nyid nor ldan rab ster dang //
T02TD3702E:336a-16: bla med mkhas pa'i grogs dang ldan pa dang //
T02TD3702E:336b-0: spro ldan stobs @336b ldan dga' zhing mang pos bkur //
T02TD3702E:336b-1: nad rnams spangs shing sems cad thams cad la //
T02TD3702E:336b-2: rjes su 'dzin zhing thos pa 'dzin pa dang //
T02TD3702E:336b-3: bsam pa dag cing bzod pa ldan pa de //
T02TD3702E:336b-4: ji srid 'jig rten phan pa 'byung ched du //
T02TD3702E:336b-5: sangs rgyas bcom ldan go 'phang bgrod gyur pa //
T02TD3702E:336b-6: de srid rtag tu yon tan 'di rnams ni //
T02TD3702E:336b-7: kun gyis brgyan pa bdag gis thob gyur cig / bcom ldan 'das ma 'phags ma nor rgyun ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD3702E:336b-8: rtog par gsungs pa'i cho gas yongs su bklags byas shing //
T02TD3702E:336b-9: 'dzin na rnam pa sna tshogs rin chen gser gyi rang bzhin gyis //
T02TD3702E:336b-10: khang pa stong phrag thams cad gang ba nyid du mdzad pa yi //
T02TD3702E:336b-11: 'jig rten kun gyi yum gyur de la gus pas phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD3702E:336b-12: lha mo khyod ni yon tan rin chen kun gyi gter chen te //
T02TD3702E:336b-13: sems can don mdzad nor dang 'bru rnams phun sum tshogs pa'i rgyu //
T02TD3702E:336b-14: do shal cod pan ldan zhing nor bu dpag bsam shing rnams kyis //
T02TD3702E:336b-15: 'jig rten gsum gyi mgon mdzad nor 'dzin nor rgyun ma la 'dud //
T02TD3702E:336b-16: nang dang 'jigs pa'i 'chi ba'i skyon mang sgrol //
T02TD3702E:336b-17: dbul ba'i sdug bsngal rma yi 'tsho byed sman //
T02TD3702E:336b-18: skal bzang gzugs kyi yon tan rigs dang rus //
T02TD3702E:336b-19: thams cad sbyin mdzad khyod kyi zhabs la 'dud //
T02TD3702E:336b-20: gang zhig yang dag bla ma'i cho gas yongs su glog byed na //
T02TD3702E:336b-21: phun tshogs yangs pa bde 'gro nye bar ster byed pa //
T02TD3702E:336b-22: nor rgyun zhes pa'i ming can gzugs de la ni dus rtag tu //
T02TD3702E:336b-23: mtha' dag sems can phan par sems pas gus pas phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD3702E:336b-24: gang zhig yang dag dran las mi rnams longs spyod yun ring du //
T02TD3702E:336b-25: rab tu 'phel zhing dbul dang nad dang sdig pa sel mdzad cing //
T02TD3702E:336b-26: dpag bsam shing dang mtshungs pa nor rgyun ming can de la'o //
T02TD3702E:336b-27: 'gro la phan pa'i ched du gus pas spyi bos phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD3702E:336b-28: bcom ldan 'das ma nor rgyun ma'i sgrub thabs dang mtshan brgya rtsa brgyad pa dang /
T02TD3702E:336b-29: smon lam dang bstod pa rnams rdzogs so /
T02TD3702E:336b-31: // / tshul 'di ni dpang lo ts'a ba dpal ldan blo gros brtan pas zhol phug tu /
T02TD3702E:336b-32: rgya dpe las bsgyur cing zhus te gtan la phab pa'i yi ge pa dang bskul ba po ni dge ba'i bshes gnyen rin chen mtha' can yin no /
